data.description: Welcome to this unique home and Bunkhouse that is less than a mile from Lake Whitney. This home is a 3 bed 2 and a half bath and 1559 sqft. Enjoy the NEW metal roof on all buildings, including garage, with a transferable warranty. The heart of this home is its inviting living room, where a grand woodburning or gas fireplace takes center stage, promising warmth and coziness on cold winter nights. The charm doesn't end there; the bunkhouse elevates your entertaining experience with a screened patio equipped with full Bluetooth capabilities. It also includes a garage as workshop, perfect for those that love DIY projects and a 2 car carport.
